cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.SY, cs.NI 

This paper discusses the development of intelligent autonomous agents for cyber defense, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also describes the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and software engineering (cs.SE) in the development of these agents. Additionally, the agents are designed to operate in a networked system (cs.SY) and specifically in military tactical networks (cs.NI).
